snippet.textDisplay: This should have 100M ... I loved how you guys gave Eng, Urdu and Roman subs. Coke Studio explorer is mind blowing idea. I am so proud of coke studio's team. I want every Pakistani to be this innovative and hard working . Plus this video is unconventionally filmed as far as pakistani music videos are usually. I loved how you moved camera, how you show them diff backgrounds like we see in international videos. Its so new in Pakistan.  As far as this song is concerned, I m addicted. Its so soothing, sounds sad yet so heart melting. Every time I listen I get goosebumps..I m soooo soooo in love with this master piece
